prompts.frontCover: An epic comic book cover illustration for a birthday card, featuring cartoon versions of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo. The scene is a vibrant, sun-drenched beach with turquoise water and golden sand. In a dynamic and humorous pose, Lao Lao is portrayed as a powerful superhero, playfully lifting Jordan above her head with one hand, showing off incredible strength. Jordan has a comically surprised and delighted expression, kicking his legs in the air. Lao Lao has a confident, laughing expression. They are both wearing the same outfits as in the photo (light blue sweatshirt for Lao Lao, tan hoodie and dark pants for Jordan, logos omitted). The background is filled with classic comic book action elements: a "KAPOW!" sound effect bubble bursts behind them, and the sun in the sky has dramatic radiating lines. In the center of the image, floating in the sky amidst the action, is the text "Happy Birthday, My Superhero!" written in a beautiful, bold, handwritten cursive script. The art style is flat 2D with thick black outlines, Ben-Day dots for shading, and a palette of bright, saturated primary colors, reminiscent of a vintage comic book.
